label: AB3_mP32_14_2e_6e-002
title: CrTe$_{3}$ Structure
comments:
We use the data taken by (Hansen, 2018) at 294K. 
 The ICSD entry is from the earlier work of (Klepp, 1982). 
 \href{current_web_home_dir/AB3_mP32_14_2e_6e-001}{Monoclinic ClFe$_{3}$} and \href{current_web_home_dir/AB3_mP32_14_2e_6e-002}{CrTe$_{3}$} have the same AFLOW prototype label, AB3\_mP32\_14\_2e\_6e. This label is similar to that of \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B_mP32_14_6e_2e-001}{$\gamma$-WO$_{3}$}, A3B\_mP32\_14\_6e\_2e. The unique structures are generated by the same symmetry operations with different sets of parameters ({\tt --params}) specified in their corresponding CIF files.
